Patch summary:
Add the desktop taskbar transparency effect and tests. The taskbar keeps normal
layout, input, and animation behavior while drawing slightly translucent in
desktop/freeform contexts.

This is isolated from the main Launcher3 desktop behavior so visual polish can
be reviewed or reverted independently from taskbar interaction fixes. The tests
cover the helper logic so future changes do not accidentally make every taskbar
transparent or lose transparency in desktop mode.

